<h1><i class="fa fa-key"></i>Protecting Links</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/sharing-files"><i class="fa fa-share"></i>Sharing Files</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-key"></i>Protecting Links</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p><%= application.name %> allows you to create links that are protected by a password.  This can be useful when you want to make a link available only to a restricted set of people. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-link"></i>Creating a Protected Link</h2>
			<p>To create a protected link, select the file or folder that you would like to share and then click "By Link" on the Share menu. Then, on the "New Link" dialog box, click the "Protection" tab. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/sharing-files/protecting-links/new-link-protection-tab.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Protection Tab on the New Link Dialog"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/sharing-files/protecting-links/new-link-protection-tab.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Protection Tab on the New Link Dialog</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-lock"></i>Accessing a Protected Link</h2>
			<p>When accessing a protected link, you will be prompted to enter a password before proceeding to the shared file or folder. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/sharing-files/protecting-links/link-password-dialog.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Link Password Dialog"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/sharing-files/protecting-links/link-password-dialog.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Link Password Dialog</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>